<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="equal-adj">equal <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'iːkwəl/    美 /'iːkwəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>相同的；同样的；相等的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>equal in size / length / height = of equal size / length / height</strong>
同等大小/长度/高度</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They believe that all work is <strong>of equal value</strong>. 
他们认为所有工作都具有同等价值。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>平等的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All human beings are equal. 
人人平等。</p><footer>外研③ – 5</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-equal-to">be equal to</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>与...相等 / 平等：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The rent was equal to half his monthly income. 
这租金相当于他半个月的收入。</p></div>

<p>2.<strong>与...同样出色；比得上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The architecture here is equal to any in the world.
这里的建筑堪与世界上任何同类建筑相媲美。</p></div>

<p>3.<strong>能胜任 (be up to)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is equal to anything. 
他无所不能。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Boys and girls are e<strong><em>_</em></strong>_, and thus they should be treated fairly.  （2006 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. equal  </p></div>